<br />
<br />I am after a devcart that doesn't need chip swapping for each build, but for MMC1.  Well, I would love to switch to MMC3, but retrousb doesn't sell MMC3 carts for fabrication.  (Someone once mentioned that the required number of gates in a PLC for MMC3 exceeded what was cost-effective or something).

		

		</td>
